{"title_page": "James Pugh (footballer)", "text_new": "{{short description|English footballer}}\n{{Multiple issues|\n{{more citations needed|date=February 2017}}\n{{no footnotes|date=February 2017}}\n}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=June 2016}}\n\n'''James Pugh'''  (born July 1891, date of death unknown) was an English [[association football|footballer]]. His regular position was at [[Defender (association football)#Full back|full back]]. He was born in [[Hereford]], [[Herefordshire]]. He played for [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]], [[Leyton Orient F.C.|Clapton Orient]], [[Coventry City F.C.|Coventry City]], [[Luton Town F.C.|Luton Town]], [[Brighton & Hove Albion F.C.|Brighton & Hove Albion]], [[Hereford United F.C.|Hereford United]], [[Bridgend Town F.C.|Bridgend Town]], [[Abertillery F.C.|Abertillery]] and [[Wrexham A.F.C.|Wrexham]].\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.mufcinfo.com/manupag/a-z_player_archive/a-z_player_archive_pages/pugh_james.html MUFCInfo.com profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pugh, James}}\n[[Category:1891 births]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Manchester United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Leyton Orient F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Coventry City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Luton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Brighton & Hove Albion F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Wrexham A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Bridgend Town A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{England-footy-defender-1890s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{more citations needed|date=February 2017}}\n{{no footnotes|date=February 2017}}\n}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=June 2016}}\n{{Use British English|date=June 2016}}\n\n'''James Pugh'''  (born July 1891, date of death unknown) was an English [[association football|footballer]]. His regular position was at [[Defender (association football)#Full back|full back]]. He was born in [[Hereford]], [[Herefordshire]]. He played for [[Manchester United F.C.|Manchester United]], [[Leyton Orient F.C.|Clapton Orient]], [[Coventry City F.C.|Coventry City]], [[Luton Town F.C.|Luton Town]], [[Brighton & Hove Albion F.C.|Brighton & Hove Albion]], [[Hereford United F.C.|Hereford United]], [[Bridgend Town F.C.|Bridgend Town]], [[Abertillery F.C.|Abertillery]] and [[Wrexham A.F.C.|Wrexham]].\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.mufcinfo.com/manupag/a-z_player_archive/a-z_player_archive_pages/pugh_james.html MUFCInfo.com profile]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pugh, James}}\n[[Category:1891 births]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Manchester United F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Leyton Orient F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Coventry City F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Luton Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Brighton & Hove Albion F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Wrexham A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Bridgend Town A.F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Year of death missing]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n\n\n{{England-footy-defender-1890s-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Red Director", "label": "safe", "comment": "Adding localshort description: \"English footballer\", overriding Wikidata description \"English footballer\" (Shortdesc helper)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Pugh_(footballer)"}
{"title_page": "Ralph Boulton", "text_new": "{{short description|English footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Use British English|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Ralph Boulton\n| image               = \n| caption             = \n| fullname            = Ralph Boulton\n| birth_date          = {{Birth date|1923|07|22|df=y}}\n| birth_place         = [[Grimsby]], England\n| death_date          = {{Death year and age|1992|1923}}\n| death_place         = \n| height              = \n| position            = [[Inside forward]]\n| youthyears1         = | youthclubs1 = \n| years1              = 1948\u20131951| clubs1 = [[Grimsby Town F.C.|Grimsby Town]]| caps1 = 3| goals1 = 0\n| years2              = 1951\u201319??| clubs2 = [[Goole Town F.C.|Goole Town]]| caps2 = | goals2 = \n}}\n\n'''Ralph Boulton''' (22 July 1923 \u2013 1992) was an [[English people|English]] professional [[association football|footballer]] who played as an [[inside forward]].<ref>{{cite book|last1=Lamming|first1=Douglas|title=A who's who of Grimsby Town AFC : 1890-1985|date=1985|publisher=Hutton|location=Beverley|isbn=0-907033-34-2|page=18}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Boulton, Ralph}}\n[[Category:1923 births]]\n[[Category:1992 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Grimsby]]\n[[Category:English footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football inside forwards]]\n[[Category:Grimsby Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Goole Town F.C. players]]\n[[Category:English Football League players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2019}}\n{{Use British English|date=December 2019}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name                = Ralph Boulton\n| image               = \n| caption             = \n| fullname            = Ralph Boulton\n| birth_date          = {{Birth date|1923|07|22|df=y}}\n| birth_place         = [[Grimsby]], England\n| death_date          = {{Death year and age|1992|1923}}\n| death_place         = \n| height  